text: Great prices on 1-for-1 bottled beers, good variety too. Unfortunately it has no seating so you have to make do with standing around or leaning on railings nearby. Love the chill atmosphere after a day of work though!
Amazing coffee for a great price (Large cappuccino for 5sgd until 11am). The barista is very friendly and quick to memorize my regular order. Every 8th coffee is free!

I've been coming here for my morning coffee the last few days and it's always been excellent. The coffee (flat white is what I usually drink) is well done and the espresso has a great taste.

The barista is also very friendly and already knows what I want.
Chill place, beers are cheaper than other bars nearby. It's a good hangout for ppl who wants a good view of the bay area and are ok with standing (although there are seats inside)
